The NDA’s landslide victory in Bihar triggered celebrations among BJP leaders and workers in Mysuru. They said the people of Bihar gave a clear mandate defeating the Mahagathbandhan in the high-stakes election, one that had drawn national attention.
Meanwhile, the BJP’s West Bengal unit has posted on X, expressing confidence that the party will win in West Bengal in the assembly polls next year. The saffron party posted on X, “Next West Bengal” with the lotus symbol.


